snippet.title: I Accidentally Became A Meme: Disaster Girl
snippet.description:
When Zoe's dad took her picture in front of a burning house, they never expected it to launch one of the most iconic memes of the decade. Learn how it went down!  Thanks to Zoe Roth, Dave Roth, Jack Brownlee and Anthony Crider  Follow Zoe at https://www.instagram.com/zoeroth/  Follow Anthony at https://www.flickr.com/photos/acrider/albums

Credits: https://www.buzzfeed.com/bfmp/videos/117596
